{"title":"npm 配置及常用命令","uid":"033e57a66d14521ced79b2223c1dfdf4","slug":"npm","date":"2021-11-10T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2021-11-10T16:00:00.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/npm.json","keywords":"Linux, LaTeX, Blog","cover":"https://img.swz128.top/npm_File/logo.png","content":"<p><svg viewBox=\"0 0 780 250\"><path fill=\"#231F20\" d=\"M240,250h100v-50h100V0H240V250z M340,50h50v100h-50V50z M480,0v200h100V50h50v150h50V50h50v150h50V0H480z M0,200h100V50h50v150h50V0H0V200z\"></path></svg></p>\n<h1 id=\"npm-配置及常用命令\"><a href=\"#npm-配置及常用命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"npm 配置及常用命令\"></a>npm 配置及常用命令</h1><h2 id=\"npm-安装\"><a href=\"#npm-安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"npm 安装\"></a>npm 安装</h2><p>详解 Node.js 中文网教程: <a href=\"http://nodejs.cn/learn/how-to-install-nodejs\">如何安装 Node.js</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"npm-常用命令\"><a href=\"#npm-常用命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"npm 常用命令\"></a>npm 常用命令</h2><ol>\n<li>查看已全局安装的包 <code>npm list -g --depth 0</code> 或者 <code>npm ls -g</code></li>\n<li><strong>安装包</strong> : <code>npm install &lt;package&gt;</code><ul>\n<li>本地安装（local）<ul>\n<li>例如: <code>npm install gulp</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>全局安装（global）,使用 -g 或 –global<ul>\n<li>例如: <code>npm install gulp -g</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>指定版本安装包 <code>npm install &lt;package&gt;@&lt;x.x.x&gt;</code><ul>\n<li>例如: <code>npm install gulp@3.9.1</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>加上 -S 或者 –save 选项,</strong> 安装包信息将加入到dependencies(生产阶段的依赖)<ul>\n<li><code>npm install gulp --save</code> 或 <code>npm install gulp -S</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>-D 或者 –save-dev 选项, 安装包信息将加入到devDependencies(开发阶段的依赖), 所以开发阶段一般使用它<ul>\n<li><code>npm install gulp --save-dev</code> 或 <code>npm install gulp -D</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>卸载模块</strong> : <code>npm uninstall &lt;package&gt;</code><ul>\n<li><code>npm uninstall [&lt;@scope&gt;/]&lt;pkg&gt;[@&lt;version&gt;]... [-S|--save|-D|--save-dev|-O|--save-optional]</code></li>\n<li>aliases: remove, rm, r, un, unlink</li>\n<li>如卸载开发版本的模块 <code>npm uninstall gulp --save-dev</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>更新模块: <code>npm update [-g] [&lt;pkg&gt;...]</code></li>\n<li>检查模块是否已经过时: <code>npm outdated [[&lt;@scope&gt;/]&lt;pkg&gt; ...]</code></li>\n<li>查看已经安装的模块: <code>npm ls [[&lt;@scope&gt;/]&lt;pkg&gt; ...]</code></li>\n<li>在项目中引导创建一个 package.json 文件: <code>npm init [-f|--force|-y|--yes]</code></li>\n<li>管理npm的配置: <code>npm config</code><pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">npm config set &lt;key&gt; &lt;value&gt; [-g|--global]\nnpm config get &lt;key&gt;\nnpm config delete &lt;key&gt;\nnpm config list\nnpm config edit\nnpm get &lt;key&gt;\nnpm set &lt;key&gt; &lt;value&gt; [-g|--global]</code></pre></li>\n<li> 最常用命令无非清除npm本地缓存: <code>npm cache clean</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"npm-换源\"><a href=\"#npm-换源\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"npm 换源\"></a>npm 换源</h2><h3 id=\"使用nrm切换镜像源\"><a href=\"#使用nrm切换镜像源\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用nrm切换镜像源\"></a>使用nrm切换镜像源</h3><ol>\n<li>下载 <code>nrm：npm install -g nrm</code></li>\n<li>查看可切换的镜像源: <code>nrm ls</code></li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">npm ---------- https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npmjs.org&#x2F;\nyarn --------- https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.yarnpkg.com&#x2F;\ntencent ------ https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.cloud.tencent.com&#x2F;npm&#x2F;\ncnpm --------- https:&#x2F;&#x2F;r.cnpmjs.org&#x2F;\ntaobao ------- https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npmmirror.com&#x2F;\nnpmMirror ---- https:&#x2F;&#x2F;skimdb.npmjs.com&#x2F;registry&#x2F;</code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>切换淘宝镜像源：<code>nrm use taobao</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"node-canvas-的安装\"><a href=\"#node-canvas-的安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"node-canvas 的安装\"></a>node-canvas 的安装</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>node-canvas模块是在node中实现canvas渲染的一种方式。可结合Echarts等应用于服务端生成图片流，进行图片处理等，如导出word或pdf时根据数据动态生成图片并嵌入文档中。下面将以Echarts为例，由服务端生成图片。</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"node-canvas安装\"><a href=\"#node-canvas安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"node-canvas安装\"></a>node-canvas安装</h3><p>node-canvas包依赖于Cairo等，需要先在系统中安装相关依赖。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>OS</th>\n<th>Command</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>OS X</td>\n<td>brew install pkg-config cairo libpng jpeg giflib</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Ubuntu</td>\n<td>sudo apt-get install libcairo2-dev libjpeg8-dev libpango1.0-dev libgif-dev build-essential g++</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Fedora</td>\n<td>sudo yum install cairo cairo-devel cairomm-devel libjpeg-turbo-devel pango pango-devel pangomm pangomm-devel giflib-devel</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Solaris</td>\n<td>pkgin install cairo pkg-config xproto renderproto kbproto xextproto</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p>安装:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">npm install canvas &#x2F;&#x2F; or yarn add canvas</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"参考\"><a href=\"#参考\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考\"></a>参考</h2><ul>\n<li>博文: <a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/syzdev/article/details/119703756\">《npm镜像源的查看和切换》</a> 作者: <a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/syzdev\">syzdev</a></li>\n<li>博文: <a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/wengye1990/article/details/71120743\">《node-canvas模块使用》</a> 作者: <a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/wengye1990\">依然自我</a></li>\n<li>博文: <a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/PeunZhang/p/5553574.html\">《npm常用命令详解》</a> 作者: <a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/peunzhang/\">白树</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"版权声明\"><a href=\"#版权声明\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"版权声明\"></a>版权声明</h2><ul>\n<li>作者：麟子</li>\n<li>地址：<a href=\"https://swz128.top/post/npm\">https://swz128.top/post/npm</a></li>\n<li>协议：<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/deed.zh\">CC BY-SA 4.0</a> 欢迎转载，务必注明出处</li>\n</ul>\n","text":" npm 配置及常用命令npm 安装详解 Node.js 中文网教程: 如何安装 Node.js npm 常用命令 查看已全局安装的包 npm list -g --depth 0 或者 npm ls -g 安装包 : npm install &lt;package&gt; 本地安...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.5k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"教程","slug":"教程","count":4,"path":"api/categories/教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"npm","slug":"npm","count":1,"path":"api/tags/npm.json"},{"name":"Node.js","slug":"Node-js","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Node-js.json"},{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":2,"path":"api/tags/JavaS